snippet.title: My Sticker Book - The game I made for the first time using Unity
snippet.description:
Game title: My Sticker Book
Available on Steam and itch.io for free

A cute and possibly just a little bit scary puzzle platformer game.
Move stickers to the right positions to get rid of the monsters in the sticker book adventure!

Story:
This is the first day the little girl sleeps on her own.
She wakes up when it is still dark and wants some water.
"But what if there are monsters hiding everywhere in the house?" She wonders...
